# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Apex CRM — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# CRITICAL SECURITY RULES:
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Variables starting with REACT_APP_ are PUBLICLY VISIBLE
# in the browser JavaScript bundle. Anyone can see them.
#
# ✅ SAFE to prefix with REACT_APP_:
#   - SUPABASE_URL (public endpoint)
#   - SUPABASE_ANON_KEY (public key, RLS protects the data)
#   - SITE_URL (your app URL)
#
# ❌ NEVER prefix with REACT_APP_:
#   - SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY (bypasses all RLS!)
#   - STRIPE_SECRET_KEY (full Stripe account access!)
#   - STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET (allows fake payment events!)
#   - RESEND_API_KEY (can send emails from your domain!)
#   - INTERNAL_API_SECRET (auth between your own functions)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── PUBLIC (safe to expose) ───────────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
REACT_APP_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=sb_publishable_...
REACT_APP_SITE_URL=https://apex-crm-jhdm.vercel.app

# ── SERVER-SIDE ONLY (never prefix with REACT_APP_) ───────────
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
STRIPE_STARTER_PRICE_ID=price_...
STRIPE_PRO_PRICE_ID=price_...
STRIPE_STARTER_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID=price_...
STRIPE_PRO_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID=price_...
RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
EMAIL_FROM=Apex CRM <noreply@yourdomain.com>
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://apex-crm-jhdm.vercel.app
INTERNAL_API_SECRET=generate_with_node_-e_require_crypto_randomBytes_32_toString_hex
CRON_SECRET=generate_with_node_-e_require_crypto_randomBytes_32_toString_hex
